The 300-year-old House of Martell hosted an exclusive event to debut their VS Single Distillery Cognac. In a private space, guests were given the opportunity to experience the distillation process of the Martell VSSD. This was followed by a tasting session by Martell Brand Ambassador Mayowa Eyitayo. With years of experience, exploration of geography, design and taste, the Martell brand has crafted a new cognac which offers a deeper taste. Guests experienced exquisite cuisine and entertainment from the likes of M.I, DO2dtun and DJ Kontroller. Other guests at the occasion were Ini Idima Okojie, Mimi Onalaja, Tobi Bakare among others.